Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,布什内尔  我们是带着礼物来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bushnell, we come bearing gifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,表达我们对你的感激之情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}tokens of our gratitude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:46.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,这都是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:49.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,一盒基度山二号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A box of Montecristo Number Twos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:50.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,一对...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A set...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:56.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,有印字的钻石袖扣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of monogrammed diamond cuff links.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, they're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有你新车的钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the keys to your new car!
