Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:13.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在你和道吉的能配成一对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now you and Dougie have a matched set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fellas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该说什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:21.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个错误被纠正了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A wrong has been made right,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,太阳明媚如初了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the sun is shining bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  伙计们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, thank you, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道发生了什么  托德先生  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I have no idea what happened, Mr. Todd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,这可太不幸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, this is most unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我同意  我不知道能说什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I agree. I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:04.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,可你知道该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们说过这事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We talked about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:10.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我给你一天时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am giving you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,去扭转局面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to remedy this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,可你之前说的是两天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you said two before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:15.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,就一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do we have a complete understanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,明白了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:35.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗杰  请进来一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Roger, get in here, please.
