Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们走  后院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go. The backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,道吉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Dougie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚你没回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When you didn't come home last night,
