Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.56,0:50:34.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我自己根本不在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I feel like I'm somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.17,0:50:37.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有过这种感觉吗  查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you ever had that feeling, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.14,0:50:40.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.51,0:50:44.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,感觉我在别处  感觉我不是自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like I'm somewhere else and--and like I'm somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.37,0:50:46.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有过这种感觉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you ever felt that?
